  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (MRL 3 variant)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. This variant operates at Model Risk Level 3. Twelve of thirteen credibility factors have been assessed; the equivalency of input parameters factor is carried as not-assessed on the basis that the modelling team judged it inapplicable to a purely computational COU with no physical test article — however the package encoding retains factorStatus 'not-assessed' rather than 'not-applicable', leaving a material epistemic gap at MRL 3.",
