      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation experiments performed on the same FDA generic pump geometry at overlapping flow-speed envelope; fluid properties within 5% of clinical blood surrogate.",
      "rationale": "Validation used the FDA generic pump geometry at matching rotational speeds but with a glycerol-water surrogate (viscosity 3.5 mPa·s vs. 3.2 mPa·s for blood surrogate). Geometric match is exact; fluid property offset exceeds 5% tolerance. Achieved level 2, below required level 3."
