      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Equivalency of input parameters",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Demonstrate that simulation input parameters (geometry, material properties, operating conditions) are equivalent between the validation case and the COU to within stated tolerances.",
      "rationale": "The modelling team determined that this factor does not apply to the present COU because the assessment is entirely computational and no physical test article is involved in the COU deployment; equivalency of input parameters is therefore considered irrelevant. Accordingly, no formal assessment was conducted and no required or achieved levels have been assigned. The factor remains not-assessed in this package."
