    "rationale": "The credibility assessment at MRL 3 is accepted on the basis that twelve of thirteen factors have been evaluated and the majority of required levels are met or closely approached. The equivalency of input parameters factor was judged by the team to be inapplicable to a purely computational COU and was therefore not assessed. All other gaps are acknowledged as manageable at the Low assurance level assigned to this COU. The package is accepted with the understanding that the unassessed factor does not materially affect the decision.",
